<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">据了解</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">“套餐A”已推出两个月</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>套餐</span></strong><strong><span>里是一份价值22元的红烧牛肉面</span></strong></span></p>
